@baseUrl = http://localhost:8888
@product = product1

### ── AUTH ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Register new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "heslo123",
  "confirmPassword": "heslo123"
}

###

### Login  (REST Client stores the Set-Cookie automatically)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "heslo123"
}

###

### Who am I?
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me

###

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout

###

### ── MARKET (public) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### List products
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/market/products

###

### Order book snapshot (top 5 levels)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/market/orderbook?product={{product}}&depth=5

###

### Trade history (last 10 snapshots)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/market/report?product={{product}}&history_len=10

###

### ── ORDERS (auth required) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Place a buy order
# @name newOrder
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product": "{{product}}",
  "side": "buy",
  "quantity": 10,
  "price": 100.0
}

###

### Get order detail  (replace ORDER_ID with value from newOrder response)
@orderId = ORDER_ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/{{orderId}}?product={{product}}

###

### Decrease order quantity
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/{{orderId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product": "{{product}}",
  "quantity": 5
}

###

### Cancel order
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/orders/{{orderId}}?product={{product}}

###

### ── ACCOUNT (auth required) ────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Balance for product
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/account/balance?product={{product}}

###

### My active orders
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/account/orders?product={{product}}

###
